---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Start Here | Grithos"
  description="Life hit you with something? Find the pillar and tenet that speaks to where you are right now. Grithos meets you where you stand."
  ogTitle="Start Here — Grithos"
  ogDescription="Map your moment to the philosophy. Whatever you're facing, there's a pillar, a tenet, and a practice for it."
  ogUrl="https://grithos.com/footing"
  canonical="https://grithos.com/footing"
  activePage="footing"
>

<style is:inline>
  /* ═══ PAGE HERO ═══ */
  .page-hero {
    padding: 80px 0 40px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .page-hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 40%; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 800px; height: 800px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(196,168,130,.05) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }
  .page-hero .wrap { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .page-hero-overline {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: .18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .page-hero-title {
    font-family: var(--heading);
    font-size: clamp(32px, 4.5vw, 52px);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .page-hero-sub {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(15px, 2vw, 18px);
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* ═══ INTRO ═══ */
  .footing-intro {
    padding: 0 0 60px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .footing-intro-text {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* ═══ SITUATIONS GRID ═══ */
  .footing-section {
    padding: 0 0 80px;
  }
  .pillar-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    padding-top: 60px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .pillar-label {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: .18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .pillar-name {
    font-family: var(--heading);
    font-size: clamp(22px, 3vw, 32px);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--white);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .pillar-tagline {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 15px;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .situation-grid {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .situation-card {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 28px 32px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all .3s;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .situation-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--gold-border);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  .situation-card.open {
    border-color: var(--gold-border);
  }

  .situation-trigger {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 16px;
    width: 100%;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 0;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .situation-label {
    font-family: var(--heading);
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1.4;
    transition: color .2s;
  }
  .situation-card:hover .situation-label {
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  .situation-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    transition: all .3s;
  }
  .situation-icon svg {
    width: 14px;
    height: 14px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    transition: all .3s;
  }
  .situation-card.open .situation-icon {
    border-color: var(--gold);
    background: var(--gold-soft);
  }
  .situation-card.open .situation-icon svg {
    color: var(--gold);
    transform: rotate(45deg);
  }

  .situation-answer {
    max-height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: max-height .4s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1), opacity .3s;
    opacity: 0;
  }
  .situation-card.open .situation-answer {
    opacity: 1;
  }
  .situation-answer-inner {
    padding: 20px 0 4px;
  }

  /* ═══ WORKFLOW STEPS ═══ */
  .workflow {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
  }
  .workflow-step {
    padding-left: 20px;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--border);
  }
  .workflow-step.active-step {
    border-left-color: var(--gold);
  }
  .workflow-step-label {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 9px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: .15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .workflow-step-title {
    font-family: var(--heading);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .workflow-step-body {
    font-family: var(--body);
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .workflow-quote {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .workflow-cite {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: .05em;
  }
  .workflow-action {
    font-family: var(--heading);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .workflow-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 16px;
  }
  .workflow-link {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: .05em;
    color: var(--gold);
    text-decoration: none;
    background: var(--gold-soft);
    border: 1px solid var(--gold-border);
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    transition: all .2s;
  }
  .workflow-link:hover {
    background: var(--gold-border);
    color: var(--white);
  }

  /* ═══ CLOSING ═══ */
  .closing {
    padding: 0 0 120px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .closing-divider {
    width: 100%;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    margin-bottom: 80px;
  }
  .closing-text {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(20px, 2.8vw, 28px);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1.5;
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto 20px;
  }
  .closing-sub {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(15px, 2vw, 18px);
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 480px;
    margin: 0 auto 40px;
  }
  .back-link {
    font-family: var(--body);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    transition: color .2s;
  }
  .back-link:hover { color: var(--gold); }
  .back-link svg { width: 14px; height: 14px; }

  /* ═══ SEARCH & FILTER BAR ═══ */
  .footing-search {
    padding: 0 0 60px;
  }
  .search-filter-wrap {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .search-box {
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .search-input {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 16px 20px 16px 52px;
    font-family: var(--body);
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--white);
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    outline: none;
    transition: border-color .2s, box-shadow .2s;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    -webkit-appearance: none;
    appearance: none;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }
  .search-input::placeholder {
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
  .search-input:focus {
    border-color: var(--gold);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(196,168,130,.15);
  }
  .search-icon {
    position: absolute;
    left: 18px;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    pointer-events: none;
    transition: color .2s;
  }
  .search-input:focus ~ .search-icon {
    color: var(--gold);
  }
  .search-clear {
    position: absolute;
    right: 14px;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    display: none;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 50%;
    transition: color .2s, background .2s;
    padding: 0;
    z-index: 3;
  }
  .search-clear:hover {
    color: var(--white);
    background: var(--border);
  }
  .search-clear.visible {
    display: flex;
  }
  .search-clear svg {
    width: 16px;
    height: 16px;
  }

  /* Autocomplete dropdown */
  .search-suggestions {
    position: absolute;
    top: calc(100% + 6px);
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    max-height: 320px;
    overflow-y: auto;
    z-index: 100;
    display: none;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.3);
  }
  .search-suggestions.open {
    display: block;
  }
  .suggestion-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 14px 20px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background .15s;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .suggestion-item:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }
  .suggestion-item:hover,
  .suggestion-item.highlighted {
    background: var(--gold-soft);
  }
  .suggestion-pillar {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 9px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: .1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    white-space: nowrap;
    padding-top: 3px;
    min-width: 70px;
  }
  .suggestion-text {
    font-family: var(--heading);
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
  .suggestion-text mark {
    background: none;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .search-no-results {
    padding: 20px;
    text-align: center;
    font-family: var(--body);
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  /* Pillar filter tabs */
  .filter-tabs {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .filter-tab {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: .06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 8px 18px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all .2s;
  }
  .filter-tab:hover {
    border-color: var(--gold-border);
    color: var(--white);
  }
  .filter-tab.active {
    background: var(--gold);
    border-color: var(--gold);
    color: var(--void);
  }
  .search-result-count {
    text-align: center;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: .06em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-top: 16px;
    display: none;
  }
  .search-result-count.visible {
    display: block;
  }

  /* Hidden states for filtering */
  .footing-section.hidden-section {
    display: none;
  }
  .situation-card.hidden-card {
    display: none;
  }

  @media(max-width: 768px) {
    .situation-card {
      padding: 22px 20px;
    }
    .situation-label {
      font-size: 15px;
    }
    .search-input {
      font-size: 16px;
      padding: 14px 16px 14px 46px;
    }
    .filter-tab {
      font-size: 10px;
      padding: 7px 14px;
    }
  }
</style>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <img src="/assets/images/grithos-logo.png" alt="Grithos" style="width: 120px; height: auto; margin-bottom: 16px; opacity: 0.85;">
    <p class="page-hero-overline reveal d1">Start Here</p>
    <h1 class="page-hero-title reveal d2">Find Your Footing</h1>
    <p class="page-hero-sub reveal d3">Five Pillars. Within each, Tenets — the principles you live by. Behind each Tenet, a Voices section — voices of those who walked this road before you. A Footing is where it all meets the ground you're standing on.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══ SEARCH & FILTER ═══ -->
<section class="footing-search">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="search-filter-wrap">
      <div class="search-box">
        <input type="search" class="search-input" id="footingSearch" placeholder="What are you facing?" autocomplete="off" inputmode="search" />
        <svg class="search-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m21 21-5.197-5.197m0 0A7.5 7.5 0 1 0 5.196 5.196a7.5 7.5 0 0 0 10.607 10.607Z" /></svg>
        <button class="search-clear" id="searchClear" aria-label="Clear search"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 18 18 6M6 6l12 12" /></svg></button>
        <div class="search-suggestions" id="searchSuggestions"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="filter-tabs">
        <button class="filter-tab active" data-filter="all">All</button>
        <button class="filter-tab" data-filter="virtue">Virtue</button>
        <button class="filter-tab" data-filter="apex">Apex</button>
        <button class="filter-tab" data-filter="control">Control</button>
        <button class="filter-tab" data-filter="death">Death</button>
        <button class="filter-tab" data-filter="verity">Verity</button>
      </div>
      <div class="search-result-count" id="resultCount"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══ PILLAR I — VIRTUE ═══ -->
<section class="footing-section" data-pillar="virtue">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="pillar-header reveal d1">
      <p class="pillar-label">Pillar I — Virtue</p>
      <h2 class="pillar-name">Do Right Regardless</h2>
      <p class="pillar-tagline">When the right thing is also the hard thing</p>
    </div>

    <div class="situation-grid">
      <div class="situation-card reveal d2">
        <button class="situation-trigger" aria-expanded="false">
          <span class="situation-label">"I lied and now it's eating me alive."</span>
          <span class="situation-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 4.5v15m7.5-7.5h-15" /></svg></span>
        </button>
        <div class="situation-answer">
          <div class="situation-answer-inner">
            <div class="workflow">
              <div class="workflow-step active-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">The Pillar</div>
                <div class="workflow-step-title">Pillar I — Virtue: Do Right Regardless</div>
              </div>
              <div class="workflow-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">The Tenet</div>
                <div class="workflow-step-title">Tenet I — Tell the Truth. Even When It Costs You.</div>
                <div class="workflow-step-body">The weight you're feeling is your own conscience doing its job. A lie held in silence doesn't stay small — it grows. The cost of telling the truth now is almost always less than the cost of carrying this forever.</div>
              </div>
              <div class="workflow-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">The Voices</div>
                <p class="workflow-quote">"If it is not right, do not do it; if it is not true, do not say it."</p>
                <div class="workflow-cite">— Marcus Aurelius, Meditations, Book XII</div>
              </div>
              <div class="workflow-step active-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">Your Practice</div>
                <p class="workflow-action">Write down exactly what the lie was and what you were afraid would happen if you told the truth. Then write one sentence — the true version of what you said. Now decide: who needs to hear it, and when? Set a time. The truth doesn't get lighter the longer you hold it.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="workflow-links">
              <a href="/tenets#tenet-i" class="workflow-link">Read Tenet I →</a>
              <a href="/voices" class="workflow-link">Read the Voices →</a>
              <a href="/practice" class="workflow-link">Today's Practice →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="situation-card reveal d3">
        <button class="situation-trigger" aria-expanded="false">
          <span class="situation-label">"I know what I should do, but it's going to cost me."</span>
          <span class="situation-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 4.5v15m7.5-7.5h-15" /></svg></span>
        </button>
        <div class="situation-answer">
          <div class="situation-answer-inner">
            <div class="workflow">
              <div class="workflow-step active-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">The Pillar</div>
                <div class="workflow-step-title">Pillar I — Virtue: Do Right Regardless</div>
              </div>
              <div class="workflow-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">The Tenet</div>
                <div class="workflow-step-title">Tenet I — Tell the Truth. Even When It Costs You.</div>
                <div class="workflow-step-body">The fact that you already know the right thing means the decision is already made — you're just stalling on the execution. The question is never really what to do. It's whether you're willing to pay for it.</div>
              </div>
              <div class="workflow-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">The Voices</div>
                <p class="workflow-quote">"You have power over your mind, not outside events. Realize this, and you will find strength."</p>
                <div class="workflow-cite">— Marcus Aurelius, Meditations, Book VI</div>
              </div>
              <div class="workflow-step active-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">Your Practice</div>
                <p class="workflow-action">Write down what you're afraid of losing. Then write down what you're losing every day you stall. You already know what to do — you said so yourself. Stop waiting for a better moment. Do the right thing today.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="workflow-links">
              <a href="/tenets#tenet-i" class="workflow-link">Read Tenet I →</a>
              <a href="/voices" class="workflow-link">Read the Voices →</a>
              <a href="/practice" class="workflow-link">Today's Practice →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="situation-card reveal d4">
        <button class="situation-trigger" aria-expanded="false">
          <span class="situation-label">"I made a promise I can't keep."</span>
          <span class="situation-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 4.5v15m7.5-7.5h-15" /></svg></span>
        </button>
        <div class="situation-answer">
          <div class="situation-answer-inner">
            <div class="workflow">
              <div class="workflow-step active-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">The Pillar</div>
                <div class="workflow-step-title">Pillar I — Virtue: Do Right Regardless</div>
              </div>
              <div class="workflow-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">The Tenet</div>
                <div class="workflow-step-title">Tenet II — Keep Your Word Like Your Life Depends on It.</div>
                <div class="workflow-step-body">You can't always keep every promise — circumstances change. But you can always be honest about it. Quietly letting a promise die is not the same as facing the person and telling them the truth. Honor still requires you to show up for that conversation.</div>
              </div>
              <div class="workflow-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">The Voices</div>
                <p class="workflow-quote">"Waste no more time arguing about what a good man should be. Be one."</p>
                <div class="workflow-cite">— Marcus Aurelius, Meditations, Book X</div>
              </div>
              <div class="workflow-step active-step">
                <div class="workflow-step-label">Your Practice</div>
                <p class="workflow-action">Contact the person before they have to follow up with you. Tell them honestly what changed. Then offer what you can actually deliver — a smaller version of the commitment, a new timeline, or a genuine apology. Don't disappear.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="workflow-links">
              <a href="/tenets#tenet-ii" class="workflow-link">Read Tenet II →</a>
              <a href="/voices" class="workflow-link">Read the Voices →</a>
              <a href="/practice" class="workflow-link">Today's Practice →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="situation-card reveal d5">
        <button class="situation-trigger" aria-expanded="false">
          <span class="situation-label">"Something went wrong and it was my fault."</span>
          <span class="situation-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 4.5v15m7.5-7.5h-15" /></svg></span>
        </button>
        <div class="situation-answer">
          <div class="situation-answer-inner">
            <div class="workflow">
              <div class="workflow-step active-step">
