                <div class="workflow-step-label">The Tenet</div>
                <div class="workflow-step-title">Tenet I — Tell the Truth. Even When It Costs You.</div>
                <div class="workflow-step-body">Notice that you're at a decision point — that's already progress. Stretching the truth is still a lie. And what you get through a lie, you have to maintain through more lies. Ask yourself whether what you want is actually worth the upkeep.</div>
