                <div class="workflow-step-title">Tenet V — Protect Those Beneath You.</div>
                <div class="workflow-step-body">Strength that only serves itself is just appetite. If you have capacity and someone in your orbit is being crushed, your inaction is a choice. The strong move when it matters.</div>
