                <div class="workflow-step-title">Tenet IV — Never Shrink. Never Apologize for Strength.</div>
                <div class="workflow-step-body">Stuck is a feeling, not a fact. Most plateaus aren't about effort — they're about a system that stopped working. Stop repeating the same move and calling it trying. Audit what you're doing and change it.</div>
              </div>
              <div class="workflow-step">
